    {
      "text": "A 9-month-old child is brought to the emergency department with parents reporting 4 days of high fever up to 39.7째C (103.5째F). Yesterday, the child had a brief episode in which they became rigid and shook for approximately 30 seconds during a fever spike. Today, the fever resolved, and a rash appeared on the trunk that is now spreading to the extremities and head. The child appears well, is interactive, and has normal vital signs. Skin examination is shown. The parents are concerned about the seizure and ask about preventing future episodes. What is the most appropriate management approach?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Prescribe a loading dose of anticonvulsant medication"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Provide reassurance and fever management education"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Refer to pediatric neurology for seizure evaluation"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Recommend aggressive fever reduction with alternating antipyretics"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Order EEG to evaluate for underlying seizure disorder"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7N04cg&anker=Zdf5779828118eec88dbfa716853e103d\" data-learningcard-id=\"7N04cg\" data-anker=\"Zdf5779828118eec88dbfa716853e103d\" data-section-id=\"TBX6Z00\" data-sememe-id=\"FnXgEA\">Loading doses</a> of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=-N0Ddg&anker=Zcd438fb2824eb980a6d8940c193890ba\" data-learningcard-id=\"-N0Ddg\" data-anker=\"Zcd438fb2824eb980a6d8940c193890ba\" data-sememe-id=\"XL09wg\">anticonvulsant</a> medications are not indicated for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Ze8c067aeadb21ddd8eba82cf945fde95\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Ze8c067aeadb21ddd8eba82cf945fde95\" data-section-id=\"TTc6Jb0\" data-sememe-id=\"MVaMEj\">simple febrile seizures</a> in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=s40tkT&anker=Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"s40tkT\" data-anker=\"Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-sememe-id=\"550ikg\">roseola infantum</a>. While the high recurrence rate may prompt consideration of preventive measures, these <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=RR0l5f&anker=Z34c7e6b1cab99047c956783229d49b59\" data-learningcard-id=\"RR0l5f\" data-anker=\"Z34c7e6b1cab99047c956783229d49b59\" data-section-id=\"qqaCzl\" data-sememe-id=\"2ZaTaQ\">seizures</a> are benign, have an excellent prognosis, and do not require prophylactic <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=-N0Ddg&anker=Zcd438fb2824eb980a6d8940c193890ba\" data-learningcard-id=\"-N0Ddg\" data-anker=\"Zcd438fb2824eb980a6d8940c193890ba\" data-sememe-id=\"XL09wg\">antiepileptic</a> therapy. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7N04cg&anker=Zdf5779828118eec88dbfa716853e103d\" data-learningcard-id=\"7N04cg\" data-anker=\"Zdf5779828118eec88dbfa716853e103d\" data-section-id=\"TBX6Z00\" data-sememe-id=\"FnXgEA\">Loading doses</a> carry unnecessary risks of medication side effects without proven benefit in preventing future <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-sememe-id=\"p50LOg\">febrile seizures</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>Correct -- <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-sememe-id=\"p50LOg\">Febrile seizures</a> occur in up to 15% of children with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=s40tkT&anker=Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"s40tkT\" data-anker=\"Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-sememe-id=\"550ikg\">roseola infantum</a> but are typically simple and benign without sequelae. Parents should be reassured about the <span data-sememe-id=\"g4WFil0\">self-limited</span> nature of the illness and educated on appropriate <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> management techniques.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>Neurological referral is not necessary for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Ze8c067aeadb21ddd8eba82cf945fde95\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Ze8c067aeadb21ddd8eba82cf945fde95\" data-section-id=\"TTc6Jb0\" data-sememe-id=\"MVaMEj\">simple febrile seizures</a> in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=s40tkT&anker=Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"s40tkT\" data-anker=\"Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-sememe-id=\"550ikg\">roseola infantum</a>. These <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=RR0l5f&anker=Z34c7e6b1cab99047c956783229d49b59\" data-learningcard-id=\"RR0l5f\" data-anker=\"Z34c7e6b1cab99047c956783229d49b59\" data-section-id=\"qqaCzl\" data-sememe-id=\"2ZaTaQ\">seizures</a> are expected complications of the high <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> and do not suggest an underlying neurological disorder.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>Aggressive <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> reduction with alternating <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Zeed7c97a9088131b8728a09585df953b\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Zeed7c97a9088131b8728a09585df953b\" data-section-id=\"CV1q9f0\" data-sememe-id=\"Kh0UUf\">antipyretics</a> has not been shown to prevent <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-sememe-id=\"p50LOg\">febrile seizures</a> and may lead to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=yq0dah&anker=Z0c6e74d0739fb94e2f3c8e5605497bbd\" data-learningcard-id=\"yq0dah\" data-anker=\"Z0c6e74d0739fb94e2f3c8e5605497bbd\" data-section-id=\"wDWhgn0\" data-sememe-id=\"JQ1sCg0\">medication errors</a>. Standard <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> management with single agents is appropriate.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Cn0qvg&anker=Z0e525243b471b6544f999eab44e59454\" data-learningcard-id=\"Cn0qvg\" data-anker=\"Z0e525243b471b6544f999eab44e59454\" data-section-id=\"xbcEDa0\" data-sememe-id=\"vMYAqp\">EEG</a> is not indicated for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Ze8c067aeadb21ddd8eba82cf945fde95\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Ze8c067aeadb21ddd8eba82cf945fde95\" data-section-id=\"TTc6Jb0\" data-sememe-id=\"MVaMEj\">simple febrile seizures</a> in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=s40tkT&anker=Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"s40tkT\" data-anker=\"Za5aea79fc55d32b41a7f19fcb2fd2f7b\" data-sememe-id=\"550ikg\">roseola infantum</a>. The <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=RR0l5f&anker=Z34c7e6b1cab99047c956783229d49b59\" data-learningcard-id=\"RR0l5f\" data-anker=\"Z34c7e6b1cab99047c956783229d49b59\" data-section-id=\"qqaCzl\" data-sememe-id=\"2ZaTaQ\">seizure</a> described is typical for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=D401lT&anker=Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-learningcard-id=\"D401lT\" data-anker=\"Z8c5fa7e82edc90ce0285896a9c72e81a\" data-sememe-id=\"p50LOg\">febrile seizures</a> in this viral illness.</div>",
